===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun}}

# An inflamed (raised and red) spot on the surface of the skin that is usually painful and fills with [[pus]].
#:''I had to pop that embarrassing '''pimple''', it was huge and on the tip of my nose''.
# {{Slang}} An annoying person.
#:''He's such a '''pimple'''! I wish he'd stop being so irritating!''

